name: Giga City Streets #1
description: Aria Vorteka - Clad in sleek, charcoal-hued attire that melds seamlessly with the night, she navigates the world's most formidable security systems with a masterful finesse. Known for her sharp intellect and a taste for the finer things in life, she's as likely to swipe a priceless painting as she is to vanish into the misty alleyways of intrigue.
